properties.headline: Gale Watch issued January 3 at 2:51PM CST until January 6 at 12:00AM CST by NWS Chicago IL
properties.description:
The National Weather Service in Chicago has issued a Gale Watch,
which is in effect from Sunday afternoon through Sunday evening.

* WINDS...West gales to 35 kt with a few gusts to 40 kt.
properties.instruction:
A Gale Watch is issued when the risk of gale force winds of 34 to
47 knots has significantly increased...but the specific timing
and/or location is still uncertain. It is intended to provide
additional lead time for mariners who may wish to consider
altering their plans.

NWSheadline: GALE WATCH IN EFFECT FROM SUNDAY AFTERNOON THROUGH SUNDAY EVENING
